@NODE Import "Things of great import"

-----------------------------------------------------------------IMPORTANT STUFF

These Icons are designed for the palette and WB style set up by
Martin Huttenloher and the MagicWorkbench package.
As all the icons I use have been gathered from the net and the fact I'm
a starving student I haven't registered *Boooo* But I Urge anyone who has
the money to do so (If you're reading this Martin, I'm getting a job
soon... so expect to hear from me.... Honest)

These Icons use the artistic discipline known as collage (AKA Uses other peoples
work :) ) and so to anyone who recognises a piece of their original artwork,
"Thank you, I hope you don't mind, If you do....please tell me"

These Icons are: 
NOTHINGISREQUIREDOFYOUIFYOUWANTTOUSETHESEICONSBUTYOUMIGHTWANTTOCHECKOUTMYWEBSITE
IFYOU'REBOREDSOMETIME-ware
I don't care WHERE these are used but if you use then commercially please
check if any bits done by other authors/esses are being shown and get
their permission too!

